description: Happy Holidays from Ultimate Surrender. This was the very first match we did. We needed to shoot a pilot match, we liked what we saw, and then U.S was born. We give this update to you as a bonus holiday update. If you not a member yet, join us now, and see what all the hype is about. Once again from the U.S. team we wish you Happy Holidays!
title: Janay and Shannon Kelly
